---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: Connected Kerry Initiative highlights transport gaps across County Kerry and the practical improvements that could make local travel easier.
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero network-bg">

  <!-- Network diagram SVG in background -->
  <svg class="hero-network" viewBox="0 0 900 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
    <!-- Route lines -->
    <line x1="650" y1="80"  x2="750" y2="200" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="750" y1="200" x2="820" y2="160" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="750" y1="200" x2="760" y2="340" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="760" y1="340" x2="680" y2="420" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="680" y1="420" x2="580" y2="380" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="580" y1="380" x2="500" y2="440" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="650" y1="80"  x2="580" y2="180" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="580" y1="180" x2="580" y2="380" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="820" y1="160" x2="870" y2="280" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="870" y1="280" x2="760" y2="340" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
    <!-- Nodes -->
    <circle cx="650" cy="80"  r="6" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="750" cy="200" r="8" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="820" cy="160" r="5" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="760" cy="340" r="7" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="680" cy="420" r="5" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="580" cy="380" r="6" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="500" cy="440" r="4" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="580" cy="180" r="5" fill="white"/>
    <circle cx="870" cy="280" r="5" fill="white"/>
  </svg>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-label">County Kerry · Ireland</span>
        <h1>Connected<br><span>Kerry</span><br>Initiative</h1>
        <p class="hero-intro">Many parts of everyday transport in Kerry are harder to see than they should be — from bus stops with no signs, to journeys that are difficult without a car, to projects that are planned but not yet visible on the ground.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/framework/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore the campaigns</a>
          <a href="/submit/" class="btn btn-secondary">Share your story</a>
          <a href="/map/" class="btn btn-secondary">View the map</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT THIS INITIATIVE DOES -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Our purpose</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">What this initiative does</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Connected Kerry Initiative is not a campaign group and does not represent any organisation. It observes, documents, and shares information about how transport works in practice across County Kerry.</p>

    <div class="what-grid">

      <div class="what-card">
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Highlights gaps</h3>
          <p>Identifies transport gaps and missed opportunities that are easy to overlook in day-to-day life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="what-card">
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="14" height="14" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="7" y1="8" x2="13" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="7" y1="12" x2="11" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Documents evidence</h3>
          <p>Gathers photographs, data, and first-hand accounts from across the county to build a clear picture.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="what-card">
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M10 3L17 7V13L10 17L3 13V7L10 3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Supports discussion</h3>
          <p>Provides clear, accessible material to support constructive conversation about local mobility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="what-card">
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 15L8 11L12 13L16 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="4"  cy="15" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
            <circle cx="16" cy="7"  r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Informs representatives</h3>
          <p>Provides digestible information for councillors, community groups, and local media.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE INVISIBLE FRAMEWORK -->
<section class="section section--subtle">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The framework</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">What's invisible in transport?</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Transport systems work best when the basics are visible — stops, routes, journeys, people, delivery, and benefits. This initiative explores where those elements are currently difficult to see.</p>

    <div class="campaigns-grid">
    {% for campaign in site.campaigns %}
      {% if campaign.status == "live" %}
      <a href="/campaigns/{{ campaign.slug }}/" class="campaign-card">
        <div class="campaign-card-top">
          <div class="campaign-icon campaign-icon--{{ campaign.colour }}">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="3"  x2="11" y2="7"  stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="15" x2="11" y2="19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="3"  y1="11" x2="7"  y2="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="15" y1="11" x2="19" y2="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="campaign-tag">Campaign theme</span>
            <h3>{{ campaign.title }}</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-card-body">
          <p>{{ campaign.summary }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-card-footer">
          Explore this theme
          <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8H13M9 4L13 8L9 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      {% else %}
      <div class="campaign-card campaign-card--soon">
        <div class="campaign-card-top">
          <div class="campaign-icon campaign-icon--{{ campaign.colour }}" style="opacity:0.45;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="3"  x2="11" y2="7"  stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="15" x2="11" y2="19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="3"  y1="11" x2="7"  y2="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="15" y1="11" x2="19" y2="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="campaign-tag">Coming soon</span>
            <h3 style="color:var(--grey-500);">{{ campaign.title }}</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-card-body">
          <p style="color:var(--grey-400);">{{ campaign.summary }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-card-footer" style="color:var(--grey-400);">
          In preparation
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BAND -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Have an example to share?</h2>
    <p>If you have spotted a transport issue in Kerry — a missing bus stop sign, a route without infrastructure, or a destination that's hard to reach — we would like to hear from you.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/submit/" class="btn btn-primary">Submit an example</a>
      <a href="/stories/" class="btn btn-secondary">Read other stories</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
